Durban duo Distruction Boyz on Tuesday announced that their album Gqom Is The Future has been certified gold. The musos known for their smash hit Omunye , shared the good news in an Instagram post, thanking fans for their support. "We'd like to thank everyone who helped us reach this mile stone and break this record. Social friends, people who bought the album, journalists, media channels, TV, radio and every single person who contributed to this. Thank you!!! (sic)" the message read. Source: The Juice